char_1118_01_24","textHome":"月咲正在购物，现在只有我一个人。@一听说海产很便宜的样子，@嗖地一下子就跑去了呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":111801,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":111801,"motion":200}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":111801,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_01_25","textHome":"呼……早上的大海真安静，只有海浪的声音。@我都不知道还有这么舒服的地方。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.3,"chara":[{"id":111801,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":111801,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":111801,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_01_26","textHome":"啊，啊呜……哼哼，月咲真是擅长做料理呢。@这鱼做得简直绝了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":111801,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":111801,"motion":200}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":111800,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1,"pos":0,"voice":"vo_char_1118_00_02","textHome":"双胞胎的妹妹，天音月咲和——@双胞胎的姐姐天音月夜。@您和我们两人同时见面还是第一次呢。@对吧，过会儿和我们一起去游泳吧！"},{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":111802,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_00_02","textHome":"双胞胎的妹妹，天音月咲和——@双胞胎的姐姐天音月夜。@您和我们两人同时见面还是第一次呢。@对吧，过会儿和我们一起去游泳吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":111802,"lipSynch":0},{"id":111800,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"id":111800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":111800,"lipSynch":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":111802,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":111801,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_01_27","textHome":"这个时间，不小心就开始想练习的事情了……@这可不行。该放松的时候就要好好放松！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":111801,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"id":111801,"motion":1}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":111801,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_01_28","textHome":"虽然知道明天也会在一起。@但是和月咲聊天太开心了，就熬夜了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":111801,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":111801,"motion":200}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":111801,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_01_29","textHome":"虽然我对游泳称不上擅长，@但是作为水名的女子，@为了不辱家世，多少还是有些心得的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":111801}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":111801,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":111801,"lipSynch":1,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_01_30","textHome":"海里出现了魔女么！？@那叫月咲……不，我一个人也没有问题。@快点把它收拾掉吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":111801,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":111801,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":111801,"motion":100}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":111801,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_01_31","textHome":"唔……好热呢……但是，这里要忍耐！@明明听说无尽镜界里面就算夏天也很凉爽……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":111801,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"id":111801,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":111801,"motion":200}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":111801,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1118_01_32","textHome":"这里是什么会场？沙滩夺旗决赛……@原来如此，在这里的人都是竞技的高手呢。"}]}